{"tid":13942,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"除咗你，全世界都拍緊拖","createTime":"2016-11-30T09:46:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T14:02:11.000Z","uid":2016,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b26143e15ac4ab19b60743e67651f6534d331696","tid":13942,"uid":2016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:46:34.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪冬天嚟到<br />\n戀愛氣息好濃厚<br />\n最近打開facebook ig <br />\n唔係求婚結婚拍拖感謝文<br />\n就係行山拍拖影合照放閃<br />\n開頭以為單身好正常<br />\n遇唔到都無辦法<br />\n點知望下身邊嘅朋友同事<br />\n其實全部都有伴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n慢慢發現其實得自己一支公<br />\n點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/Ishc7WVemuJKU/source.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FIshc7WVemuJKU%2Fsource.gif&h=8dd1c9b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本來都無乜嘢<br />\n但最近真係太多情侶Post <br />\n唯有上嚟叫下春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正評：同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負評：有拖拍個班仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac1cdf578fc4a4598cb0d0771065076c7c7d00a0","tid":13942,"uid":17140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:47:42.000Z","msg":"我username<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b3578f55d1d679dcf0473ecac0e7e0f8fabe16","tid":13942,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:48:37.000Z","msg":"Sad"},{"pid":"e54fa15d519d0a90986a9259175820756de1e9d8","tid":13942,"uid":2016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:51:41.000Z",